<div class="grid-3">
  <div class="box" style="padding:var(--s-6);">
    <h3 style="font-size:var(--fs-md);margin-bottom:var(--s-2);">Native Compilation</h3>
    <p style="font-size:var(--fs-sm);color:var(--c-text-secondary);margin:0;">
      Compiles to native machine code via LLVM with O2 optimization. No VM, no interpreter, no JIT.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="box" style="padding:var(--s-6);">
    <h3 style="font-size:var(--fs-md);margin-bottom:var(--s-2);">Garbage Collected</h3>
    <p style="font-size:var(--fs-sm);color:var(--c-text-secondary);margin:0;">
      Thread-safe mark-and-sweep GC with conservative stack scanning and O(1) pointer lookup.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="box" style="padding:var(--s-6);">
    <h3 style="font-size:var(--fs-md);margin-bottom:var(--s-2);">Rich Type System</h3>
    <p style="font-size:var(--fs-sm);color:var(--c-text-secondary);margin:0;">
      Static typing with generics, nullable types, isinstance checks, and full type inference.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="box" style="padding:var(--s-6);">
    <h3 style="font-size:var(--fs-md);margin-bottom:var(--s-2);">LSP Server</h3>
    <p style="font-size:var(--fs-sm);color:var(--c-text-secondary);margin:0;">
      Diagnostics, completion, hover, go-to-def, references, rename, formatting, inlay hints, and semantic tokens.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="box" style="padding:var(--s-6);">
    <h3 style="font-size:var(--fs-md);margin-bottom:var(--s-2);">Package Manager</h3>
    <p style="font-size:var(--fs-sm);color:var(--c-text-secondary);margin:0;">
      Declare deps in vsl.toml, resolve with MVS, fetch from Git. No central registry needed.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="box" style="padding:var(--s-6);">
    <h3 style="font-size:var(--fs-md);margin-bottom:var(--s-2);">Standard Library</h3>
    <p style="font-size:var(--fs-sm);color:var(--c-text-secondary);margin:0;">
      math, string, collections, I/O, random, datetime, json, network, and system modules.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
